graph LR
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelMesh -->|state management| etcd[etcd 3.x<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelMesh -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|metrics CRD| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|model storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>ODH/RHOAI]
    ModelMesh -.->|mTLS & authz| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH/RHOAI Dashboard] -->|model deployment UI| ModelMesh

    %% Kubernetes Platform
    ModelMesh -->|CRD storage & orchestration| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    ModelMesh -->|image pulls| Registry[Container Registry]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    subgraph "Model Runtimes (One or more)"
        Triton[Triton Server 2.x]
        MLServer[MLServer 1.x]
        OpenVINO[OpenVINO Model Server 1.x]
        TorchServe[TorchServe 0.x]
    end

    ModelMesh -->|runtime containers| Triton
    ModelMesh -->|runtime containers| MLServer
    ModelMesh -->|runtime containers| OpenVINO
    ModelMesh -->|runtime containers| TorchServe

    %% External Services
    subgraph "External Services"
        S3Service["AWS S3 / MinIO / Ceph"]
        PVC["Persistent Volume Claims"]
        HTTPEndpoints["HTTP/HTTPS Endpoints"]
    end

    ModelMesh -.->|model artifacts| S3Service
    ModelMesh -.->|model artifacts| PVC
    ModelMesh -.->|model artifacts| HTTPEndpoints

    %% Styling
    style ModelMesh fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies
    style etcd fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style PrometheusOp fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal dependencies
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Platform
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Registry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Runtimes
    style Triton fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333
    style MLServer fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333
    style OpenVINO fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333
    style TorchServe fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333

    %% External services
    style S3Service fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style PVC fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style HTTPEndpoints fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
